### 1) Registro de usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "prueba76@example.com",
  "password": "contrasenia1234"
}

### 2) Validación de email
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/user/validation
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5ZDI2NGJhNDRmNWY2MWNlMjNmODEzMSIsImlhdCI6MTc3NTM5NjAyNiwiZXhwIjoxNzc1Mzk2OTI2fQ.B0B1Eis9AkloFSLfmx3v8tw41jHqbaVU3-TVOPtaj6Q
